<!-- Title -->
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>HELP US HELP CHILDREN AND FAMILIES</strong></h2>
<!-- Paragraphs -->
<p>WAPF is working to address the issue of Paternity Fraud by educating the public through our media campaigns and bringing about effective and positive legislative changes through our advocacy programs. All children deserve to know the identity of their biological fathers, their medical history, and if they are eligible for inheritance rights. Today there is DNA testing and no excuse for continued injustice for families.</p>
<p>Please help fund our efforts and make a difference by giving to WAPF!<br /> <strong>Women Against Paternity Fraud (WAPF) is a 501(c)(3) tax exempt, nonprofit organization. All donations are tax-deductible to the extent permitted by law.</strong></p>
